# Scaffold templates: markdown carries {{handle}}/{{rosterTable}}/{{channel}} tokens
# (and a {{handle}}.md path-token file) that `anthill init` renders verbatim.
# Prettier must NOT reflow these — the rendered docs/team output must stay byte-identical.
templates/

# NOTE: `docs/` is intentionally NOT ignored — we want the main knowledge folder
# consistently formatted. The prose-mangle risk (a hand-wrapped line starting with
# `+`/`-`/`*` being read as a stray bullet) only bites under prose *reflow*; we run
# prettier with the default `proseWrap: preserve`, so line breaks are left alone. The
# load-bearing agent docs that must stay byte-stable live under `.anthill/` (below),
# not `docs/`, so the formatter stays off them.

# Generated / vendored
node_modules
dist

# anthill team footprint (living docs + config.json) — keep the host formatter off the
# pheromone docs and the JSON config (a **/*.json glob would rewrite it).
.anthill/
